    "Once all hypergradients have been calculated, serialized training parameters Θ are no longer needed and can be discarded.",
    "Therefore, a more typical storage complexity is O(pT) or O(np)-both of which are still substantial.",
    "∇ L(z i; (t-1)).",
    "HyDRa and TracIn share many of the same strengths.",
    "For example, HyDRa does not require assumptions of convexity or stationarity."
